// JANUS phase-1 operational planning. COA generation is deliberately isolated so
// a future LLM adapter can replace the local deterministic generator without
// changing operation data, validation, snapshots or document generation.
const OPERATION_TASKS=["主攻","助攻","予備","火力支援","防空","ISR","電子戦","海上支援","航空支援","兵站","戦略予備"];
